ėHAROLD ARTHUR DUDMAN:
MARCH 5TH 1923 - JUNE 6TH 2009
FREEMAN OF THE CITY OF LONDON,
WANDSMAN OF
ST. PAUL'S CATHEDRAL

[Second inscription added 2019]
ALSO HIS BELOVED WIFE
OF 58 YEARS
EDITH IRENE (LESLEY) DUDMAN
JANUARY 26TH 1926 - MARCH 24TH 2019
REUNITED FOR ETERNITY"Ě
ö[SEAT BACK]
WILLIAM McLEAN MUSICIAN 1904 - 1989
BELOVED HUSBAND OF JOY McLEAN (Prof. Kn' as SANDRA WELLS) 

[UNDER SEAT]
REMEMBERED IN SO MANY HEARTS"ě
õIn appreciation of the joy and harmony
These beautiful gardens have given us
For over 40 years of our stay
In Farm Street
Donated by Kert & Peiya Kumar"•
ĘCHARLES JAMES GREGORY CHURCH
OCTOBER 1942 JULY 1989
MAY HIS MEMORY LIVE IN THIS BEAUTIFUL GARDEN
DEDICATED BY THE WELCOME WILSON, JUNIOR FAMILY
HOUSTON. TEXAS"•
